profile.primary_concern: accessing medication consistently while managing mental health

context: As a woman living with schizophrenia, I often find it challenging to focus on my health needs, especially when it comes to accessing PrEP. The stigma around my condition makes me hesitant to discuss my sexual health, and I worry about how my medication might interact with PrEP. I'm also concerned about my ability to remember to take the medication regularly, given my mental health challenges.
